    {
        "content": "<p>I believe it should be true, yes. To prove this you can apply <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=Finset.equivOfCardEq#doc\">docs#Finset.equivOfCardEq</a> to <code>h</code> and then use <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=Finset.card_bij#doc\">docs#Finset.card_bij</a> and explicitly give a bijection, or you could prove <code>(S.piAntidiag n).card = (S.card + n - 1).choose n</code></p>",
